getAppCacheBusterParameters.description: Returns the AppCacheBuster URL parameters needed for running an application with AppCacheBuster

params.name: sFilePath
params.description: File Path of the file that is being run

params.name: sOffset
params.description: relative offset of the running file

returns.description: Array of the URL parameters for for running an application with a AppCacheBuster. For example [{"name":"sap-ui-appCacheBuster", "value":"../"}]
